{"title":"CppFunctions","slug":"CCpp_functions","date":"2022-07-19","updated":"2023-02-23","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/12049.json","excerpt":"<blockquote><p> 总结了 C++ 常用函数 </p></blockquote>","cover":null,"covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>总结了 C++ 常用函数</p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"C- 函数总结\"><a href=\"#C- 函数总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"C++ 函数总结\"></a>C++ 函数总结</h1></blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"判断大小写\"><a href=\"# 判断大小写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"判断大小写\"></a>判断大小写</h2></blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 用来判断一个字符是否为字母，如果是字符则返回非零，否则返回零。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">1.</span><span class=\"built_in\">isalpha</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 用来判断一个字符是否为数字或者字母，也就是说判断一个字符是否属于 a~z||A~Z||0~9。是返回非零，不是返回 0。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">2.</span><span class=\"built_in\">isalnum</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 用来判断一个字符是否为小写字母，也就是是否属于 a~z。是返回非零，不是返回 0。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">3.</span><span class=\"built_in\">islower</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 用来判断一个字符是否为大写字母。是返回非零，不是返回 0。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">4.</span><span class=\"built_in\">isupper</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//a 为字符时，如果 a 是小写字母则将其转换为大写字母，否则不变。a 为数字则将其按 ASCLL 码转换为对应字符。（其实即使 a 是字符，输入之后还是会将其转换为 int 类型）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">5.</span> <span class=\"type\">char</span> c = <span class=\"built_in\">toupper</span>(a)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//a 为字符时，如果 a 是大写字母则将其转换为小写字母，否则不变。a 为数字则将其按 ASCLL 码转换为对应字符。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">6.</span><span class=\"type\">char</span> c=<span class=\"built_in\">tolower</span>(a)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 用来判断一个字符是否为数字，如果是数字则返回非零，否则返回零。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">7.</span><span class=\"built_in\">isdigit</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 将数字转换为字符串，这里注意如果是浮点型数转字符，会将精度范围内小数点后的数全部显示出来 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">8.</span><span class=\"built_in\">to_string</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 数字转字符串：例如：</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">float</span> b = <span class=\"number\">2.</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">s = <span class=\"built_in\">to_string</span>(b);</span><br><span class=\"line\">cout &lt;&lt; s&lt;&lt;<span class=\"string\">&quot; &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;s.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 输出为：<span class=\"number\">2.000000</span> <span class=\"number\">8</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"字符串\"><a href=\"# 字符串\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符串\"></a>字符串</h1><blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"字符串的一些常用操作\"><a href=\"# 字符串的一些常用操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符串的一些常用操作\"></a>字符串的一些常用操作</h2></blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// count 删了之后只替换一个字符</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">str.<span class=\"built_in\">replace</span>(index,count,instead) -&gt;<span class=\"type\">void</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 重载很多，startIndex 默认为 0，从字符串下标为 0 开始找</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">str.<span class=\"built_in\">find</span>(tagetStr,startIndex) -&gt; first_index</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"字符串的复制和拼接\"><a href=\"# 字符串的复制和拼接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符串的复制和拼接\"></a>字符串的复制和拼接 </h2>  <figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">  strcpy 函数进行字符串的复制</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 将 first_name 复制给 full_name</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">strcpy</span>(full_name, first_name);   </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">strcat</span>() 函数进行字符串的拼接</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 将 last_name 拼接在 full_name 之后</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">strcat</span>(full_name, last_name);   </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 字符与字符串之间可以用 + 来连接</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  string s; <span class=\"type\">char</span> ch;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  s = s + ch;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"字符串与整数的转换\"><a href=\"# 字符串与整数的转换\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符串与整数的转换\"></a>字符串与整数的转换</h2><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// nums 为字符串，stoi 函数存在于头文件 &lt;string&gt; 中</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> k = <span class=\"built_in\">stoi</span>(nums);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// num 为整数，to_string 函数也在 string 中</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">string s=<span class=\"built_in\">to_string</span>(num)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"字符与整数的互换\"><a href=\"# 字符与整数的互换\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符与整数的互换\"></a>字符与整数的互换</h2><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 字符转整数，直接强转</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">char</span> c=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;8&#x27;</span> ;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> a ;</span><br><span class=\"line\">a =(<span class=\"type\">int</span>) (c - <span class=\"string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>) ;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 整数转字符</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> b;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">char</span> c;</span><br><span class=\"line\">c = b + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"algorithm- 函数中的 reverse\"><a href=\"#algorithm- 函数中的 reverse\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"algorithm 函数中的 reverse\"></a>algorithm 函数中的 reverse</h1><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">reverse 无返回值 </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">str.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>() 是指向 str 的第一个元素 </span><br><span class=\"line\">str.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>() 是指向最后一个元素的后一个位置</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">1.</span><span class=\"built_in\">reverse</span>(str.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(),str.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>()) 反转整个字符串</span><br><span class=\"line\"> \t </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">2.</span><span class=\"built_in\">reverse</span>(vector.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(),vector.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>()) 反转向量</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">3.</span><span class=\"built_in\">reverse</span>(a,a+<span class=\"built_in\">strlen</span>(a)) 反转数组</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","url":"/posts/12049/","min2read":2,"word4post":684,"prev_post":{"title":"Notes","url":"/posts/52648/"},"next_post":{"title":"CppHeadFiles","url":"/posts/56443/"},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"C- 函数总结\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">C++ 函数总结</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"判断大小写\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">1.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">判断大小写</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"字符串\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">字符串</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"字符串的一些常用操作\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">字符串的一些常用操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"字符串的复制和拼接\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">字符串的复制和拼接 </span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"字符串与整数的转换\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.3.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">字符串与整数的转换</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"字符与整数的互换\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.4.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">字符与整数的互换</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"algorithm- 函数中的 reverse\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">algorithm 函数中的 reverse</span></a></li></ol>","categories":[{"name":"C/CPP","path":"api/categories/C/CPP.json","url":"/categories/C-CPP/"}],"tags":[{"name":"functions","path":"api/tags/functions.json","url":"/tags/functions/"}]}